Class RoleServiceImp

java.lang.Object

All Implemented Interfaces:
RoleService
@Service
public class RoleServiceImp
extends java.lang.Object
implements RoleService
The implementation of the role service. It interacts with the different roles using a role repository, modifying directly on the database.
